    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. it feels like the \"economic boost\" argument is always used by politicians but it doesn't really help the actual business owners on the ground. do you think there's any way for a small business to actually survive these hikes without just cutting staff or raising prices so much that they lose customers?",
