    "summary": "The user is asking for economic advice regarding the impact of minimum wage increases on a hypothetical small rural coffee shop. The assistant provides a series of responses that lean heavily toward the perspective that wage hikes are a net negative for small businesses, focusing on increased costs and diminished profitability while framing the opposing \"economic boost\" view as largely theoretical or less impactful in practice.",
